Description: Pi Camera 3 raw YUV420 UDP server for Raspberry Pi 5
 Streams uncompressed YUV420 frames from multiple Pi Camera 3 modules
 over UDP. Supports dual-stream (main + lores), instant camera switching,
 and lux telemetry.
 .
